==English==

===Noun===
(like•li•hood)
The probability of a specified outcome.<br>
#[[probability]]; The state of being [[probable]].
#:''In all '''likelihood''' the meeting will be cancelled.''
#:''The '''likelihood''' is that the inflation rate will continue to rise.''

